Patch Set 8: Code-Review+1

A question has come up about the doc impact.  This will affect the OpenStack Configuration Reference.  The relevant page is generated here:

https://github.com/openstack/openstack-manuals/blob/c0d4b3f222481854541743ae0eada1ae4396aec3/doc/config-reference/image-service/section_image-service-sample-configuration-files.xml#L49

So as long as we get our stable/liberty branch cut before the docs team generates the stable/liberty branch of the manuals, the change will get into the Liberty manuals.  Otherwise it will show up in the drafts branch.  So from the docs point of view, this change doesn't cause any extra work for them, it's up to us to get it merged in time if we want it to appear in the manual.
